</li>
<li data-section-id="1j3vxn8" data-start="1714" data-end="1720">
<p data-start="1716" data-end="1720">Java</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="yhmts0" data-start="1721" data-end="1725">
<p data-start="1723" data-end="1725">AI</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1727" data-end="1778">make your profile look serious and growth-oriented.</p>
<hr data-start="1780" data-end="1783">
<h1 data-section-id="1n7985r" data-start="1785" data-end="1814">Main Weaknesses (Important)</h1>
<p data-start="1816" data-end="1853">The internship specifically mentions:</p>
<ul data-start="1854" data-end="1904">
<li data-section-id="rvusbz" data-start="1854" data-end="1867">
<p data-start="1856" data-end="1867">Spring Boot</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="3mxeoj" data-start="1868" data-end="1879">
<p data-start="1870" data-end="1879">REST APIs</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1o4hle" data-start="1880" data-end="1885">
