</li>
<li data-section-id="hbffsy" data-start="1886" data-end="1904">
<p data-start="1888" data-end="1904">backend services</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1906" data-end="1961">but your resume currently does not show these directly.</p>
<p data-start="1963" data-end="2014">This does NOT mean you are rejected.<br>
It just means:</p>
<blockquote data-start="2015" data-end="2085">
<p data-start="2017" data-end="2085">your resume is slightly mismatched for backend Java roles right now.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="2087" data-end="2090">
<h1 data-section-id="zpn6ie" data-start="2092" data-end="2141">What You Should Do Immediately (Very Important)</h1>
<p data-start="2143" data-end="2159">Before applying:</p>
<h2 data-section-id="19w4p4v" data-start="2161" data-end="2205">Add These Skills ONLY if you know basics:</h2>
<ul data-start="2206" data-end="2304">
<li data-section-id="1dv721b" data-start="2206" data-end="2217">
<p data-start="2208" data-end="2217">Core Java</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1v4ejt7" data-start="2218" data-end="2232">
<p data-start="2220" data-end="2232">OOP Concepts</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="f1yju9" data-start="2233" data-end="2247">
<p data-start="2235" data-end="2247">Git &amp; GitHub</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="3mxeoj" data-start="2248" data-end="2259">
<p data-start="2250" data-end="2259">REST APIs</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1j3wrdz" data-start="2260" data-end="2266">
<p data-start="2262" data-end="2266">JDBC</p>
</li>
