</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2306" data-end="2309">
<h1 data-section-id="151fn9v" data-start="2311" data-end="2347">BEST THING YOU CAN DO IN 7–10 DAYS</h1>
<p data-start="2349" data-end="2385">Build ONE small Spring Boot project.</p>
<p data-start="2387" data-end="2395">Example:</p>
<ul data-start="2396" data-end="2473">
<li data-section-id="1q6q5xm" data-start="2396" data-end="2420">
<p data-start="2398" data-end="2420">Student Management API</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1rjc26l" data-start="2421" data-end="2432">
<p data-start="2423" data-end="2432">To-Do API</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ubgy5q" data-start="2433" data-end="2452">
<p data-start="2435" data-end="2452">Notes App Backend</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ijquad" data-start="2453" data-end="2473">
<p data-start="2455" data-end="2473">Login/Register API</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2475" data-end="2484">Features:</p>
<ul data-start="2485" data-end="2512">
<li data-section-id="1o4gwu" data-start="2485" data-end="2490">
<p data-start="2487" data-end="2490">GET</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1j4al8w" data-start="2491" data-end="2497">
<p data-start="2493" data-end="2497">POST</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1o4obd" data-start="2498" data-end="2503">
<p data-start="2500" data-end="2503">PUT</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1uxxenl" data-start="2504" data-end="2512">
<p data-start="2506" data-end="2512">DELETE</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2514" data-end="2523">Then add:</p>
<blockquote data-start="2524" data-end="2561">
<p data-start="2526" data-end="2561">“Built REST APIs using Spring Boot”</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="2563" data-end="2578">to your resume.</p>
<p data-start="2580" data-end="2632">That single line can massively improve your chances.</p>
<hr data-start="2634" data-end="2637">
<h1 data-section-id="lzri1a" data-start="2639" data-end="2675">Your Resume Also Needs Improvement</h1>
<p data-start="2677" data-end="2753">Your current resume looks visually good, but technically it needs polishing.</p>
