<hr data-start="3054" data-end="3057">
<h1 data-section-id="1e3uk5t" data-start="3059" data-end="3074">Final Verdict</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="2ttrfr" data-start="3076" data-end="3095">Current Chances:</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="igun4l" data-start="3096" data-end="3138">Small startups / learning internships:</h3>
<p data-start="3139" data-end="3152">✅ Good chance</p>
<h3 data-section-id="yjvu12" data-start="3154" data-end="3189">Proper Java backend internship:</h3>
<p data-start="3190" data-end="3218">⚠️ Moderate chance currently</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1v03grk" data-start="3220" data-end="3263">After learning basic Spring Boot + Git:</h3>
<p data-start="3264" data-end="3306">✅ Very good chance for student internships</p>
<hr data-start="3308" data-end="3311">
<h1 data-section-id="lzj56u" data-start="3313" data-end="3351">What Recruiters Will Think About You</h1>
<p data-start="3353" data-end="3377">Probably something like:</p>
<blockquote data-start="3378" data-end="3517">
<p data-start="3380" data-end="3517">“This student is motivated, participates actively, has good communication and projects, but needs stronger backend development exposure.”</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="3519" data-end="3587">And honestly, for a BCA 2nd-year student:<br>
that is completely normal.</p>
<p data-start="3589" data-end="3636">You are already ahead of many students because:</p>
<ul data-start="3637" data-end="3744">
<li data-section-id="mng586" data-start="3637" data-end="3668">
<p data-start="3639" data-end="3668">you participate in hackathons</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ss2nrv" data-start="3669" data-end="3689">
<p data-start="3671" data-end="3689">you build projects</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1pldrpj" data-start="3690" data-end="3715">
<p data-start="3692" data-end="3715">you care about learning</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1avvc9" data-start="3716" data-end="3744">
<p data-start="3718" data-end="3744">you have direction in tech</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="3746" data-end="3749">
