v></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex justify-end"><div aria-label="Your message actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto touch:opacity-100 duration-300 group-hover/turn-messages:delay-300 pointer-events-none opacity-0 motion-safe:transition-opacity group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:opacity-100 group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:opacity-100 has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:opacity-100" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy message" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-16f983c9.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Edit message" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-16f983c9.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></section></div><div class="" data-turn-id-container="e232511d-fba0-4f81-ae01-a42154762aa0" data-is-intersecting="true"><section class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto R6Vx5W_threadScrollVars scroll-mb-[calc(var(--scroll-root-safe-area-inset-bottom,0px)+var(--thread-response-height))] scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" dir="auto" data-turn-id="e232511d-fba0-4f81-ae01-a42154762aa0" data-turn-id-container="e232511d-fba0-4f81-ae01-a42154762aa0" data-testid="conversation-turn-736" data-turn="assistant"><h4 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div data-conversation-screenshot-content="" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="e232511d-fba0-4f81-ae01-a42154762aa0" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-5" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="46">Good questions. Here's the short answer first:</p>
<ul data-start="48" data-end="255">
<li data-section-id="1tqli7l" data-start="48" data-end="111">
<p data-start="50" data-end="111"><strong data-start="50" data-end="100">Do I need to open WSL every time I use Docker?</strong> → <strong data-start="103" data-end="111">❌ No</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1tj0idm" data-start="112" data-end="165">
<p data-start="114" data-end="165"><strong data-start="114" data-end="154">Do I need to open Ubuntu every time?</strong> → <strong data-start="157" data-end="165">❌ No</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="9bjx57" data-start="166" data-end="255">
<p data-start="168" data-end="255"><strong data-start="168" data-end="193">What if I delete WSL?</strong> → <strong data-start="196" data-end="255">⚠️ Docker Desktop (Linux containers) will stop working.</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="257" data-end="281">Now let's go one by one.</p>
<hr data-start="283" data-end="286">
<h2 data-section-id="10rm8ne" data-start="288" data-end="316">1. Do I need to open WSL?</h2>
<p data-start="318" data-end="325"><strong data-start="318" data-end="325">No.</strong></p>
<p data-start="327" data-end="340">Just do this:</p>
<ol data-start="342" data-end="437">
<li data-section-id="f6o4fc" data-start="342" data-end="368">
<p data-start="345" data-end="368">Open <strong data-start="350" data-end="368">Docker Desktop</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="q8azro" data-start="369" data-end="409">
<p data-start="372" data-end="409">Wait until it says <strong data-start="391" data-end="409">Engine running</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1s0s59c" data-start="410" data-end="437">
<p data-start="413" data-end="437">Run your Docker commands</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="439" data-end="449">That's it.</p>
<p data-start="451" data-end="496">WSL runs <strong data-start="460" data-end="481">in the background</strong> automatically.</p>
<hr data-start="498" data-end="501">
<h2 data-section-id="s1tx2k" data-start="503" data-end="534">2. Do I need to open Ubuntu?</h2>
<p data-start="536" data-end="542">Again,</p>
<p data-start="544" data-end="551"><strong data-start="544" data-end="551">No.</strong></p>
<p data-start="553" data-end="606">Ubuntu is just a Linux distribution that WSL can run.</p>
<p data-start="608" data-end="698">Unless you specifically want to use Linux commands, you never need to open the Ubuntu app.</p>
<p data-start="700" data-end="720">For your internship:</p>
<ul data-start="722" data-end="784">
<li data-section-id="1p3j5l1" data-start="722" data-end="733">
<p data-start="724" data-end="733">VS Code ✅</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1jv2z8r" data-start="734" data-end="752">
<p data-start="736" data-end="752">Docker Desktop ✅</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="sy54qo" data-start="753" data-end="784">
<p data-start="755" data-end="784">Command Prompt / PowerShell ✅</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="786" data-end="796">is enough.</p>
<hr data-start="798" data-end="801">
<h2 data-section-id="wektgh" data-start="803" data-end="838">3. Then why is Ubuntu installed?</h2>
<p data-start="840" data-end="877">Because Docker uses Linux internally.</p>
<p data-start="879" data-end="901">Think of it like this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="903" data-end="990"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-16f983c9.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>You</span><br><span> │</span><br><span> ▼</span><br><span>Docker Desktop</span><br><span> │</span><br><span> ▼</span><br><span>WSL</span><br><span> │</span><br><span> ▼</span><br><span>Ubuntu (Linux)</span><br><span> │</span><br><span> ▼</span><br><span>Docker Engine</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="992" data-end="1043">You normally interact only with <strong data-start="1024" data-end="1042">Docker Desktop</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1045" data-end="1048">
<h2 data-section-id="o4zdx" data-start="1050" data-end="1090">4. What happens if you uninstall WSL?</h2>
<p data-start="1092" data-end="1159">If Docker is configured to use WSL (the default on modern Windows):</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1161" data-end="1242"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-16f983c9.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>No WSL</span><br><span>    ↓</span><br><span>No Linux</span><br><span>    ↓</span><br><span>No Docker Engine</span><br><span>    ↓</span><br><span>Docker won't start</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1244" data-end="1323">So <strong data-start="1247" data-end="1270">don't uninstall WSL</strong> if you're using Docker Desktop for Linux containers.</p>
<hr data-start="1325" data-end="1328">
<h2 data-section-id="ng8zye" data-start="1330" data-end="1365">5. Do I have to learn Linux now?</h2>
<p data-start="1367" data-end="1383">Not immediately.</p>
<p data-start="1385" data-end="1448">For now, you only need a few commands later in your internship:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1450" data-end="1490"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="relative h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="select-none sticky z-2 top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-16f983c9.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Bash</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-16f983c9.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>pwd</span><br><span class="ͼ10">ls</span><br><span class="ͼ10">cd</span><br><span class="ͼ10">mkdir</span><br><span class="ͼ10">rm</span><br><span class="ͼ10">cp</span><br><span class="ͼ10">mv</span><br><span class="ͼ10">cat</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1492" data-end="1521">That's enough to get started.</p>
<hr data-start="1523" data-end="1526">
<h2 data-section-id="t2d13y" data-start="1528" data-end="1559">6. Your workflow from now on</h2>
<p data-start="1561" data-end="1589">Whenever you work on Docker:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1591" data-end="1746"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-16f983c9.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>1. Turn on your laptop</span><br><br><span>2. Open Docker Desktop</span><br><br><span>3. Wait until "Engine running"</span><br><br><span>4. Open VS Code</span><br><br><span>5. Open Command Prompt</span><br><br><span>6. Run Docker commands</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1748" data-end="1791"><strong data-start="1748" data-end="1791">No need to manually open WSL or Ubuntu.</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1793" data-end="1796">
<h2 data-section-id="18m1f0k" data-start="1798" data-end="1829">7. When WILL you use Ubuntu?</h2>
<p data-start="1831" data-end="1893">Probably later in your internship when you start working with:</p>
<ul data-start="1895" data-end="1994">
<li data-section-id="1cc33c8" data-start="1895" data-end="1920">
<p data-start="1897" data-end="1920">AWS EC2 (Linux servers)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1vdc3xq" data-start="1921" data-end="1947">
<p data-start="1923" data-end="1947">SSH into remote machines</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="oicivn" data-start="1948" data-end="1973">
<p data-start="1950" data-end="1973">Docker Compose on Linux</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="rx1etp" data-start="1974" data-end="1994">
<p data-start="1976" data-end="1994">Deployment scripts</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1996" data-end="2084">But for the assignments you've done so far, <strong data-start="2040" data-end="2083">you don't need to open Ubuntu even once</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="2086" data-end="2089">
<h3 data-section-id="vy2chn" data-start="2091" data-end="2112">My recommendation</h3>
<p data-start="2114" data-end="2322" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node=""><strong data-start="2114" data-end="2138">Leave WSL installed.</strong> It's lightweight, Docker depends on it, and you'll almost certainly use it later when you get into cloud deployment. Think of it as infrastructure rather than an app you actively use.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-16f983c9.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" heigh