-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="38">ER stands for <strong data-start="14" data-end="37">Entity Relationship</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="40" data-end="56">So when I wrote:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="58" data-end="77"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-16f983c9.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>ERD.png</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="79" data-end="87">I meant:</p>
<ul data-start="89" data-end="154">
<li data-section-id="1hjoyto" data-start="89" data-end="128">
<p data-start="91" data-end="128"><strong data-start="91" data-end="98">ERD</strong> = Entity Relationship Diagram</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="15yc7mu" data-start="129" data-end="154">
<p data-start="131" data-end="154"><strong data-start="131" data-end="139">.png</strong> = Image format</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="156" data-end="204">So it's simply an image of your database design.</p>
<p data-start="206" data-end="249">For your assignment, your folder should be:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="251" data-end="437"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-16f983c9.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Database Design</span><br><span>│</span><br><span>├── database.sql</span><br><span>├── ERD.png          ← The image I generated for you</span><br><span>├── Output.png       ← Screenshot of pgAdmin output</span><br><span>├── Explanation.docx</span><br><span>├── README.md</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="439" data-end="445">Where:</p>
<ul data-start="447" data-end="692">
<li data-section-id="48t031" data-start="447" data-end="481">
<p data-start="449" data-end="481"><strong data-start="449" data-end="465">database.sql</strong> → Your SQL code</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1xdoi4u" data-start="482" data-end="542">
<p data-start="484" data-end="542"><strong data-start="484" data-end="495">ERD.png</strong> → The database diagram (the image I generated)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="14pkopt" data-start="543" data-end="608">
<p data-start="545" data-end="608"><strong data-start="545" data-end="559">Output.png</strong> → Screenshot showing your tables/data in pgAdmin</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="x7joqm" data-start="609" data-end="654">
<p data-start="611" data-end="654"><strong data-start="611" data-end="631">Explanation.docx</strong> → One-page explanation</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="12yvx1w" data-start="655" data-end="692">
<p data-start="657" data-end="692"><strong data-start="657" data-end="670">README.md</strong> → Project description</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="694" data-end="785" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">So <strong data-start="697" data-end="746">ERD.png is just the name of the diagram image</strong>, not a special type of folder or file.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-16f983c9.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-16f983c9.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use